Package: MultiATSM
Type: Package
Title: Multicountry Term Structure of Interest Rates Models
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2021-10-08
Author: Rubens Moura
Maintainer: Rubens Moura <rubens.gtmoura@gmail.com>
Description: This Package Provides Estimation Routines for Several Classes of Affine Term Structure of Interest Rates Models. All the Models Are Based on the Unspanned Macroeconomic Risk Framework from Joslin, Priebisch, and Singleton (2014). 
